---
title: Chicken & Artichoke Cassoulet with Herbed Breadcrumbs & Mozzarella
description: We've taken cassoulet - a traditionally slow-cooked French bean casserole - and made it delicious in under 35 minutes. You'll get the same richness from thyme-roasted tomatoes, caramelized onion, and marinated chicken. Oh, and let's not forget about that cheesy breadcrumb topping. This sure ain't your Momma's casserole!
